    <arm_group_label>Motivational Interviewing for Change of Parenting Styles</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>After measured parental style across the scale, the motivational interviewing will be applied in order to modify the parenting styles of risk for involvement with drug use and maintenance of protective factors. This approach will occur in 5 segments .</description>
